  Locus:
    Page: 432
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Simplicity
---
Our purpose in life is to realize the Self. It is an easy matter to get a
little food and find somewhere congenial to live and meditate. Once we have
achieved this we should have no further interest in the world and its
problems.
